description: Sky Force unravels a gripping story inspired by extraordinary true events surrounding one of the deadliest airstrikes between India and Pakistan. This epic tale of bravery and sacrifice follows the mystery of a hero lost in action and a comrade`s relentless quest for the truth. Packed with emotion, camaraderie, and high-stakes action, Sky Force is a soaring tribute to courage and resilience!
